        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/cma-to-investigate-online-gaming-companies-roll-over-contracts">CMA to investigate online gaming companies’ roll-over contracts</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
