          </li>
          <li>
            Check <a href="/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=competition-and-markets-authority&publication_type=foi-releases" class="brand__color">our previous releases</a> to see if we’ve already answered your question.
          </li>
            <li>Make a new request by contacting us using the details below.</li>
        </ol>

